      "text": "I want to talk about a writer who's obviously been extremely important to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.64,
      "end": 9.48,
      "text": "He was the guiding spirit behind the 48 laws of power, undoubtedly."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.88,
      "end": 12.64,
      "text": "And that is my good friend, Niccolò Machiavelli."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.6,
      "end": 22.0,
      "text": "Machiavelli, I remember also kind of sound like I was."
    }
